<p>
<note n="0072001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0072001">語＝說【宋】</note>
<note n="0072002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0072002">唯＝惟【三】【宮】下同</note>
<note n="0072003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0072003">（答）＋有【明】</note>
<note n="0072004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0072004">健＝犍【三】</note>
<note n="0073001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0073001">所＝於【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0073002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0073002">摽＝標【三】【宮】＊</note>
